Title: Welcome to » DVD Laser Scanner Microscope
Description: The laser scanning microscope is a special light microscope which uses a focused laser beam to scans the sample. The scanning of the laser across the sample is done by driving the laser in x and y direction.  The image is composed in the software by combining the measured light points.
